Columns: 31;
                                                  ruled lines: 18;
                                                  written lines: 18; Uniform layout. Ruling by hard point,
membrane by membrane.Visible stiching of membranes. Hair side and flesh side of membranes distinguishable. Three tagin on שעטנזגץ and one on בדהחיפף. A few majuscular or minuscular letters, ח being also arched. The names of the sons of Haman arranged in 11 lines, in accordance with the rule. Wooden roller (155mm high).
